data.description: This gorgeous 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom is a 70West built home located in Peyton's Ridge, one of Onslow County's most eagerly sought-after communities in Hubert. Features of the home are high-end finishes like the wood flooring, crown molding, coffered ceilings, soft close cabinetry, stunning countertops, glass subway tile backsplash, and an oversized kitchen island with additional seating. On the second floor, you'll enjoy the flex space that separates the main bedrooms from the remaining guest bedrooms. This space could easily be used as a media room, home office, or a homeschool room. The master bedroom includes a spacious bathroom with individual oversized vanities, a large shower and a huge walk-in closet. The spacious guest bedrooms are opposite the flex space. With a large indoor and outdoor space and MOVE-IN ready, this home is sure to not last long on the market. Check out the 3D Tour for a more personal experience of this home. Some photos are digitally altered.
